These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, traveling, baking
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, coral, purple
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, manager, software-developer
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, car, subway
3 different games are played: go, scrabble, poker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, amaryllis
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, art-deco
 1. the person playing go is the person who likes coral##1
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 3. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 4. the dancer is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the cape-cod house is between the person who likes purple and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 8. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes coral is between the person who growsbegonia and the person playing scrabble##2
10. the person driving the car is the manager##1
11. the cape-cod house is between the person driving the subway and the person who growsamaryllis##2
12. the cape-cod house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
13. the art-deco house is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |         3          |
| Hobby      | baking | writing     | traveling      |
| Color          | light-blue | coral | purple               |
| Job           | dancer   | manager   | software-developer |
| Transport   | scooter  | car | subway           |
| Game   | scrabble  | go   | poker               |
| Flower   | amaryllis  | zinnia   | begonia           |
| House           | gothic-revival   | cape-cod      | art-deco              |

