.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, lime, onion
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, fanta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, scientific, documentary
House: art-deco, craftsman, wooden
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, sunflower
3 different games are played: whist, scrabble, go
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, car, motorbike
 1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 2. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 3. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
 4. the person watching spy movies is the person playing go##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the person eating apple##1
 8. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating apple is on the right of the craftsman house##1
10. the person who growszinnia is the person watching spy movies##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growssunflower##1
12. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
13. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
14. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
15. the person playing whist is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Food          | lime     | apple      | onion      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate    | fanta  | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre           | scientific | documentary   | spy |
