 3. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 4. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of jazz is between the person who likes pink and the person who growsazalea##2
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 9. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the person traveling to boston##1
11. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

