There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, brown, apricot
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, vegafina, chaman
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, puzzles
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, sailing
House: modern, wooden, townhouse
 1. the person who likes apricot is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the modern house is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the wooden house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the wooden house is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Flower      | amaryllis   | dahlia      | azalea      |
| Birthday          | november | september      | august      |
| Color           | apricot  | brown  | emerald    |
