.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, coral, yellow
City: boston, berlin, marseilles
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, spy
3 different games are played: backgammon, go, billiard
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, water, hot-chocolate
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, goldfish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, april
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person playing go##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 5. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 6. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is the person watching spy movies##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the owner of the rat is the person traveling to berlin##1
13. the person drinking water is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3      |
| Color         | coral | aquamarine           | yellow    |
| City           | berlin     | marseilles | boston |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | spy             | animation  |
| Game   | backgammon     | billiard           | go  |
| Beverage   | water    | hot-chocolate      | juice   |
| Pet         | rat    | frog      | goldfish |
| Birthday     | march   | april            | may        |

