There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, mexican
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, davidoff, aristoff
House: cottage, gothic-revival, palace
 1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
 3. the person watching superhero movies is between the gothic-revival house and the person who growsrose##2
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the chinese is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the palace house##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 9. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
11. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |       3       |
